  "detailed_description": "When we were young, have we all dreamed of the world of mini humankind? <br />\r\nThis game will satisfy your fantasy. You will become a man/woman smaller than a rabbit, going through time and space through a magical stone door, and come to the mini-world island.<br />\r\nYou need to find your airship (though smaller than a rabbit), then find and visit other 4 mini human civilizations, while at the same time you will need to repel the attacks from a dragonfly army.",
